by dayofr at 2016-11-05T07:58:01Z

`order_by` feels a lot like SQL.
`sort` feels more natural.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by javiereguiluz at 2016-11-05T09:46:10Z

OK, let's keep this option as `sort` to not give the impression that you can use the same syntax as SQL `order_by`. Thanks!
